Average accuracy: {{ $('Merge Data').item.json.stats.avgAccuracy }}%
Total practice time: {{ $('Merge Data').item.json.stats.totalMins }} mins

Session details:
{{ JSON.stringify($('Merge Data').item.json.weekSessions) }}

Agent decisions this week:
{{ JSON.stringify($('Merge Data').item.json.weekDecisions) }}

