Respond ONLY in this exact JSON format, no markdown:
{
  "summary": "3-5 sentence parent-friendly summary",
  "escalation_flag": true or false,
  "escalation_reason": "one sentence or empty string",
  "therapist_draft": "brief therapist update or empty string",
  "next_week_focus": "one sentence recommendation"
}
